stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> STOPPED

    STOPPED --> BOOTING : Start Button / bootVirtualMachine()
    BOOTING --> RUNNING : Process Started & Streams Open
    BOOTING --> ERROR : Process Fail / Exit != 0

    RUNNING --> STOPPED : Stop Button / process.destroy()
    RUNNING --> STOPPED : VM Internal Shutdown / exitCode 0
    RUNNING --> ERROR : Process Crash / Exit != 0

    ERROR --> STOPPED : Reset / Clear Logs
    ERROR --> BOOTING : Retry
